reviews.review_text:
Clarence Clemons Too! Thanx Russ.  This is a great upgrade from my cassettes.  The overall bass tones are somewhat thin.  I love the Bird Song & Blow Away.
Clarence appears from Aiko thru Truckin' and then again for lovelight & Brokedown.  He generally doesn't add much.  A great show to be at, especially the Fogerty set.
I am opening my radio show with Bird Song and Space thru Lovelight this week.  Peace
